Package com.robo.messaging

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Message<TContent>
    Defines a message
    MessageBus
    Intended for exchanging messages.
    MessageRepository  
    PublisherCallback
    Callback interface for the message bus to interact with publisher.
    PublishingStrategy<TMessage extends Message>
    Strategy for publishing messages.
    Subscriber<TMessage extends Message>
    Defines a subscriber that receives messages of a specified type.
    SubscriptionToken
    A subscription token for identifying subscription of a subscriber.
    TokenGenerator
    Intended for generating subscription tokens.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractMessage<TContent>
    The base class for implementing messages.

    Provides implementation of MessageRepository, stores historic messages in memory.
    MessageBusImp
    Default implementation of MessageBus.
    UUIDToken
    A token based on UUID.
    UUIDTokenGenerator
    Generates token based on UUID.
  • Enum Summary

    ThreadOption
    Specifies which thread used for publishing messages.
